115
00:06:26,100 --> 00:06:28,960
Mrs. Coleman,Ribocore will do
everything we can to help you.

116
00:06:28,960 --> 00:06:30,640
Everything? What are you doing

117
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:32,280
